00:47:41,943 --> 00:47:45,943
Within 20 minutes, 75...

303
00:47:48,663 --> 00:47:51,503
million tons of ice break free.

304
00:47:58,843 --> 00:48:02,383
Glaciers have always released ice into the ocean,

305
00:48:03,683 --> 00:48:09,023
but now this is happening nearly twice as fast as it did ten years ago.

306
00:48:12,283 --> 00:48:17,743
Around the world, ice is now feeding vast amounts of freshwater into the sea,

307
00:48:17,743 --> 00:48:24,203
raising sea levels, changing salinity, and disrupting ocean currents.

308
00:48:27,703 --> 00:48:32,963
Without the Humboldt Current, the coast of Peru would fall silent.

309
00:48:32,963 --> 00:48:45,383
The seabird spectacle would be no more.

310
00:48:49,223 --> 00:48:54,023
All across our planet, crucial connections are being disrupted.

311
00:48:54,023 --> 00:49:03,203
The stability that we and all life relies upon is being lost.

312
00:49:06,743 --> 00:49:09,703
What we do in the next 20 years

313
00:49:09,703 --> 00:49:24,083
will determine the future for all life on Earth.

